title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today’s Dan Patrick Show, Dan reacts to the Golden State Warriors winning another NBA title. DP talks to Reggie Miller about whether Steph Curry has broken into the NBA Top 10 all-time players. Chris Mannix and DP debate about the league being positionless.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
